{"tid":2411305,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商經局研推通行卡限人群活動","createTime":"2021-02-17T08:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T08:46:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"624d8d139b86c1303d8d8259ffcd211bd1e6ec64","tid":2411305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/VEG6WREEVRBCHI6X45KR3PQG4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FVEG6WREEVRBCHI6X45KR3PQG4Q%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN221VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=4c96d6ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FVEG6WREEVRBCHI6X45KR3PQG4Q%2F&h=3b585426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/VEG6WREEVRBCHI6X45KR3PQG4Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n商經局研推通行卡限人群活動<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國各省自去年起實行「健康碼」制度，以紅、黃、綠三種顏色顯示市民染疫風險，有侵害私隱之嫌，惟港府打算與內地看齊。商經局長邱騰華昨接受商台專訪時透露，政府正考慮逐步引入類似互認「通行卡」的安排，令經貿活動在疫情下安全進行。民主黨主席羅健熙批評，港府「自主地去抄」內地抗疫措施，對疫情毫無幫助。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：賞你遊加碼 或資助staycation<br />\n<br />\n商經局長邱騰華在專訪中表示，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DpMpxDlxhFTipzldnsIFs7WkphE=/5040x3360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G5PTN6KH5VB7JBJSG7HYICPHJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDpMpxDlxhFTipzldnsIFs7WkphE%3D%2F5040x3360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG5PTN6KH5VB7JBJSG7HYICPHJY.jpg&h=4a21ef2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■商經局長邱騰華透露政府考慮引入「通行卡」安排，恢復經貿活動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅健熙斥照抄內地無助抗疫<br />\n<br />\n邱更透露，港府正考慮逐步引入類似互認「通行卡」的安排，透過加強病毒檢測及管理人群等，令一些大型展覽等經貿活動能在疫情下安全進行，但未有解釋計劃詳情及何時實施。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席羅健熙炮轟，通行卡做法「嘥氣」，目的只為搜集市民的出行紀錄，對抗疫根本沒有任何幫助。<br />\n<br />\n羅健熙又批評，港府往往「自主地去抄」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n前立法會議員毛孟靜亦質疑，對通行卡互認做法感不理解，「點樣互認，到時係咪又要市民拎身份證呢，唔係好明」。她又認為，港府近月的抗疫措施似向內地「交功課，所謂從祖國學習囉，呢啲嘢有冇用，香港人心裏有數啦」。<br />\n<br />\n商經局回覆查詢時亦未有解釋計劃，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a1ef0b5fed38e93e4e0213f1ab19f1b82b28ecc7","tid":2411305,"uid":59922,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:41:17.000Z","msg":"直接社會信用評分啦，扮乜撚嘢"},{"pid":"bd646dffda30b18c529899c46f6d64ac56f8107c","tid":2411305,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c018bdfc8bb54b9b878f4c59b942ad0ed297bfd6","tid":2411305,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"高級獸印 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc1786f13f9c6f36afbd39fc3edd63e4c7f6ad6","tid":2411305,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:46:59.000Z","msg":"炒撚咗你自己先啦"}]}